arently in friendship."}, {"version": "pearl", "text": "They work in large colonies and make rings by linking their tails, apparently in friendship."}, {"version": "platinum", "text": "Split into two, the tails are so adept at handling and doing things, AMBIPOM rarely uses its hands."}, {"version": "soulsilver", "text": "It is very difficult to dodge the consecutive strikes of its two tails."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "It uses its tails for everything. If it wraps both of its tails around you and gives you a squeeze, that\u2019s proof it really likes you."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "In their search for comfortable trees, they get into territorial disputes with groups of Passimian. They win about half the time."}, {"version": "white", "text": "Split into two, the tails are so adept at handling and doing things, Ambipom rarely uses its hands."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "Split into two, the tails are so adept at handling and doing things, Ambipom rarely uses its hands."}, {"version": "x", "text": "They work in large colonies and make rings by linking their tails, apparently in friendship."}, {"version": "y", "text": "To eat, it deftly shucks nuts with its two tails. It rarely uses its arms now."}], "entryGameVersions": ["alpha-sapphire", "black", "black-2", "diamond", "heartgold", "legends-arceus", "omega-ruby", "pearl", "platinum", "soulsilver", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun", "white", "white-2", "x", "y"], "moveGameGroups": ["black-2-white-2", "black-white", "brilliant-diamond-shining-pearl", "diamond-pearl", "heartgold-soulsilver", "legends-arceus", "omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire", "platinum", "scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon", "x-y"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "aipom"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "ambipom"}]}